author: Jack Tonhaben
title: Saudi Journalist Tells Palestinians That Arab World Is Losing Interest In Their Cause
text: A Palestinian protester flashes the sign for victory as he holds stones in his hands during clashes with Israeli security forces near the Beit El settlement on the outskirts of Ramallah in the West Bank, on October 14, 2015. The rising tide of violence, which has seen a series of stabbing attacks and protests, has raised fears of a full-scale third Palestinian intifada, or uprising.
